{"tid":2201640,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"姜丹尼爾 被選為想像戀人一樣在\"拍照日\"裡一起拍照的明星第一位","createTime":"2020-09-14T03:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T07:52:29.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"863671f0ecd8325351023473163ef0846c5b7186","tid":2201640,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RrtzOe7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRrtzOe7.jpg&h=84ff0079&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n8月17日至9月10日，小學、初中、高中網絡數學教育企業seven edu以3,469人為對象進行了輿論調查，結果顯示，姜丹尼爾（2,194人，63.2%）被選為想像戀人一樣一起拍紀念照的明星一位。<br />\n第二位是樸寶劍（937名，27.0%），其後依次是金秀賢（138名，4.0%）和防彈少年團金泰亨（44名，1.3%）。<br />\n&quot;拍照日&quot;是9月14日，是戀人一起拍照留念的日子。對於姜丹尼爾被選為在&quot;拍照日&quot;像戀人一樣想一起照紀念照的明星第一位的原因，榜單相關人士分析稱&quot;這可能是因為姜丹尼爾溫暖的外貌和似打扮又似沒打扮的時尚，展現了男友照的定式&quot;。<br />\n另外，姜丹尼爾在8月SBS《人氣歌謠》的舞台結束後，結束了《Color Project》第二張迷你專輯《MAGENTA》的正式音樂放送活動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca0fe3b910ccec2fb587559179a4463698f93b5","tid":2201640,"uid":68678,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:21:48.000Z","msg":"造馬團centre 果然唔同啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38b214baff9a2c898b44eafd1dc1376bc06188b0","tid":2201640,"uid":205928,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:26:52.000Z","msg":"死姜狗幾時od死"},{"pid":"be07ebbaecc1d68c23c8e20a20a01af8b4320ead","tid":2201640,"uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"38b214baff9a2c898b44eafd1dc1376bc06188b0","tid":2201640,"uid":205928,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T03:26:52.000Z","msg":"死姜狗幾時od死"},"citedBy":2,"replyT